{"tid":1008950,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［26］ P牌 買車 上路一問","createTime":"2019-02-04T22:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T06:55:40.000Z","uid":84508,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d7bd1e3e57305806e2a089942261869af5bcadf7","tid":1008950,"uid":84508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T22:59:09.000Z","msg":"P牌 應該買二手定新車好？<br />\n買二手怕買伏車有排執 唔識睇<br />\n買新車怕跌車 <br />\n筆值60k  高168<br />\n同埋保險點搞24歲 有揸開46 屋企車<br />\n睇中ninja 400<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋P牌上路面有咩應該要注意？<br />\nThanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d27dc380d18ca6dcf98d1ab483d921bf46ca314","tid":1008950,"uid":55032,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T23:29:12.000Z","msg":"父幹撚 唔會玩得掂26 <br />\n<br />\n16幾就唔好諗咁多啦  你預呢世大車都唔會岩你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6650cb7166db74a89cd5626c3a16372d4968c707","tid":1008950,"uid":84508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7d27dc380d18ca6dcf98d1ab483d921bf46ca314","tid":1008950,"uid":55032,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T23:29:12.000Z","msg":"父幹撚 唔會玩得掂26 <br />\n<br />\n16幾就唔好諗咁多啦  你預呢世大車都唔會岩你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T23:32:54.000Z","msg":"你叻 你威<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d534e064f216b4e53a5b32f3264ae87b02c42efa","tid":1008950,"uid":23249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T01:38:40.000Z","msg":"我果陣新牌出左部aprilia, 兩皮野only<br />\n同你一樣唔識睇二手驚伏<br />\n亦都係驚新手出車好快炒<br />\n所以就出呢部<br />\n貪佢低馬力120cc 易控<br />\n同埋佢都幾細部，你既高度應該冇問題<br />\n我建議你可以考慮下入手呢類平d 細部d 既先，真係ok 再換部好d 既，因為26 既二手市場都幾硬淨，賣返出去唔會蝕好多"},{"pid":"3b7e20e0c7c12e2c5781d67da7d1f432b0cc697d","tid":1008950,"uid":91873,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:01:55.000Z","msg":"買部300，400cc 細車玩下先<br />\nNinja 300,400/r3/mt系都係幾好選擇（自己認為）<br />\n易上手，易保養，